    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i guess. but it's more than just being \"broken\". it's like... i see people living their lives and it feels like i'm watching a movie in a language i don't speak. there's no point in trying to learn it if i'm never gonna actually be part of it. it just feels like i'm wasting time existing.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
